-- Other Media Detection
In this agent will be able to detect media , not only text
media : gif , sticker [ plain , animated , lottie animated] , image , video , 1 send

---------------------------------------------------------
-- Mouse Movement
All over the whatsapp whether from send to click or hover it will simulate real humanized path.
Till now it did not had any human mouse path, only robotic way of directly clicking

